### URI base da API
@apiurl = http://localhost:8080/chess/api

### Join a client
POST {{apiurl}}/clients/ HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "Nuno"
}

### Get all clients
GET {{apiurl}}/clients/ HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Leave a client
DELETE {{apiurl}}/clients/Nuno HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json